	(text "Audio Sync Detection\n\nPurpose:\n  Convert analog audio events into clean digital edges for \n  precision timestamping by STM32.\n\nSignal Path:\n  DAC Out -> AC Couple -> Rectify -> Envelope -> Schmitt\n\nTiming Semantics:\n  Rising edge = audio energy begins\n\nHysteresis prevents chatter from noise\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
